			<img src="../templates/massarbeit/template_thumbnail.png" style="margin-right: 1em; float: left" />
			<p><strong>Description:</strong> massarbeit is a Clean and Professional Free Joomla! 1.7 Template designed for the Joomla! Community.</p>
